title: Vegan Day
typeOfFood: Vegan, American, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern
description: A small vegan cafe and shop located in an old historical center. Serves falafel, burgers, sandwiches, hot dogs, and more. Beverages include coffee, tea and other non-alcoholic drinks. Sells fodstuffs to cook at home such as tofu, cheese, sausage, cutlets, nuts and groats, plus vitamins and other things. Est. 2015.
